[normal] 
[normal]Taken as a whole, we have actually reduced a lot of the 
[normal]ring
[normal]­
[normal]fencing
[normal] and direct specification of funding inside local government.
[normal] 
[normal]If you compare that against the amount by which we reduced 
[normal]ring
[normal]­
[normal]fencing
[normal] and specific grants, that would far outweigh whatever we have done in relation to 
[normal]holdback
[normal].
[normal]              [bold]Heather Wheeler:[bold] Chairman, indulge me.
[normal] 
[normal]When was the last time any of you guys sat down and helped set a district council’s budget for five years?
[normal] 
