[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Q18 [bold]&#xa0; 
[normal]John Pugh:[bold] When do you expect the interruption to be lifted?
[normal]Peter Schofield[bold]: We are looking to see the interruption lifted as soon as possible.
[normal] 
[normal]As I say, we have now, to the auditors’ satisfaction, addressed all of the issues that they first raised.
[normal] 
