[normal]Sir Bob [bold]Kerslake[bold]: We have a power to fund, and we have the power to support them in capitalising the expenditure.
[normal] 
[normal]Ultimately, we have the power to intervene and take over services, as has happened, but that has not been required in very many cases.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Q26 [bold]&#xa0; 
