[normal]Sir Bob [bold]Kerslake[bold]: In terms of capitalisation, that has been a feature of a number of years where we have allowed local authorities to bid for the ability to capitalise the expenditure.
[normal] 
[normal]We have intervened
[normal]—in a very limited way, 
[normal]a
[normal]s you will be aware, of course—
[normal]in 
[normal]Doncaster
[normal].
[normal] 
