[normal]Peter Schofield[bold]: We have looked at the fact that the cost side of the equation is also lower, for the reasons I have described.
[normal] 
[normal]Our view is that, overall, this should be something that is manageable for local authorities, and for many, the balance will be a net reduction in the overall 
[normal]burden that they have from this.
[normal] 
